{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778905084530,"sessionID":"ses_1d1028ea2ffevSTrimEHvR87Mj","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:22","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","content":"Thank you for raising this issue. I have revised the definition of **cardiac septum (UBERON:0002099)** to cover all of its child terms, including the interatrial septum, interventricular septum, outflow tract septum, atrioventricular septum, and aortico-pulmonary spiral septum.\n\nThe previous definition was limited to septa between the two atria or the two ventricles, which did not accurately reflect the full scope of the term's children in the ontology. The updated definition now reads:\n\n> \"A septum that is part of the heart and divides parts of the heart, including the atria, ventricles, and outflow tract.\"\n\nThis mirrors the existing logical definition (septum + part_of heart) while being broad enough to encompass all child terms. A `term_tracker_item` linking back to this issue has also been added to the term.\n\nChanges committed in PR #<NN>.\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778905084521,"end":1778905084527}},"id":"prt_e2f0153cf0011ne0jveS8kL7x8","sessionID":"ses_1d1028ea2ffevSTrimEHvR87Mj","messageID":"msg_e2f014840001Z8v8WOl3ZvABQe"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778905109532,"sessionID":"ses_1d1028ea2ffevSTrimEHvR87Mj","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:23","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md","content":"## Summary\n\nThis PR updates the textual definition of **UBERON:0002099 (cardiac septum)** to accurately cover all of its child terms in the ontology.\n\n## Problem\n\nThe previous definition of cardiac septum was:\n\n> \"The thin membranous structure between the two heart atria or the thick muscular structure between the two heart ventricles.\"\n\nThis definition was too narrow and did not account for several child terms, including:\n- **outflow tract septum** (UBERON:0004142)\n- **atrioventricular septum** (UBERON:0005989)\n- **aortico-pulmonary spiral septum** (UBERON:0006207)\n\nAdditionally, the previous definition incorrectly characterized all cardiac septa as either \"thin membranous\" or \"thick muscular,\" which does not apply uniformly across all children (e.g., the aortico-pulmonary spiral septum is muscular but not described by the original definition).\n\n## Changes Made\n\n1. **Revised definition of UBERON:0002099:**\n   - **Old:** \"The thin membranous structure between the two heart atria or the thick muscular structure between the two heart ventricles.\"\n   - **New:** \"A septum that is part of the heart and divides parts of the heart, including the atria, ventricles, and outflow tract.\"\n   - The new definition mirrors the existing logical definition (`intersection_of: UBERON:0003037 ! septum` + `intersection_of: part_of UBERON:0000948 ! heart`) and is broad enough to cover all child terms.\n\n2. **Added `term_tracker_item`:**\n   - Added a `property_value: term_tracker_item` linking back to GitHub issue #3003 for provenance tracking.\n\n## Validation\n\n- Confirmed all child terms of UBERON:0002099 using `obo-grep.pl` to verify the scope of the term.\n- Verified that the revised definition is consistent with the logical definition and the parent term **septum** (UBERON:0003037: \"A wall, dividing a cavity or structure into smaller ones\").\n- No other terms were modified; child term definitions were reviewed and found to be individually accurate.\n\n## Checklist\n\n- [x] Reviewed child terms of UBERON:0002099\n- [x] Drafted broader definition aligned with logical definition\n- [x] Edited `terms/UBERON_0002099.obo`\n- [x] Checked term back into `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`\n- [x] Added `term_tracker_item`\n- [x] Verified git diff\n- [x] Committed changes\n\nSigned-off-by: dragon-ai-agent\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"PR_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778905109524,"end":1778905109530}},"id":"prt_e2f017304001ruUipD4aasgwGF","sessionID":"ses_1d1028ea2ffevSTrimEHvR87Mj","messageID":"msg_e2f014840001Z8v8WOl3ZvABQe"}}
